{"tid":1174971,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Supper Moment 七一出席維穩show","createTime":"2019-05-28T08:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T03:18:53.000Z","uid":189721,"like":40,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"941a57764a2c51d002f78e25caf11e6ee73882bf","tid":1174971,"uid":189721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:46:24.000Z","msg":"今年7月1日有「維穩騷」在銅鑼灣維多利亞公園舉行，意味七一遊行將再次不可在維園起步。據悉，相關活動名稱為「Greater Bay Festival 2019」（簡稱「大灣區節」），由香港各界慶典委員會聯同香港匯演藝能發展中心合辦，6月29日（周六）至7月1日（周一）一連3日舉辦，邀請到韓國天王鄭智薰（Rain）、DJ Soda、前NBA球星Jason Williams及馬貝利、台灣歌手周興哲、本地樂隊Supper Moment及Dear Jane等演出。資料顯示，活動獲民政事務總署支持。"},{"pid":"3aaf34de52a562c8dffe43d04cb5a011798606df","tid":1174971,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aeeb45b361d04011c178ed3bb909f85ddd29c7","tid":1174971,"uid":228995,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:09:45.000Z","msg":"Rubberband 同mr都試過中招啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804060d1dbdae9a0baf1b060c22a07e3be06e824","tid":1174971,"uid":50041,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:10:50.000Z","msg":"大灣區節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"649f41964dc67fb43d76981b2dd9a0b1d137f9d9","tid":1174971,"uid":157368,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"ByeBye SM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a2a204c0e9d1